msgid "Control how WooCommerce coupons and Discount Tools rules interact. Both Active: allow both to apply simultaneously. Coupons Only: disable plugin discounts when any coupon is used. Discount Tools Only: prevent customers from using coupons (plugin rules take priority)."
msgstr "控制 WooCommerce 优惠券和折扣工具规则的互動方式。两者皆启用:允许同時应用。仅优惠券:使用任何优惠券時停用外掛折扣。仅折扣工具:防止客戶使用优惠券(外掛规则优先)。"

